title.narrative: Nepal: Grid Solar and Energy Efficiency

description.narrative: The project development objectives (PDOs) are to: (i) increase solar photovoltaic generated electricity to supply to the NEA grid; and (ii) reduce NEA's distribution losses in selected distribution centers.
